e,"text":"The baseline design establishes the\ncritical path: client keystroke flows\nthrough WebSocket to a stateful\nCollab Node, is OT-transformed,\nappended to the op log, then\nbroadcast to all peers in the doc.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3M","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"The baseline design establishes the\ncritical path: client keystroke flows\nthrough WebSocket to a stateful\nCollab Node, is OT-transformed,\nappended to the op log, then\nbroadcast to all peers in the doc.","height":112.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1088537341,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":371,"angle":0,"y":-1155.5390624999991,"width":260.9097900390625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#fed7aa","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3N","backgroundColor":"#5C3D1A","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"zZGDB1rEzfODCa0RD4O6R","x":371,"seed":886347379,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"4EDl9H41rFwkwm0VCK9qE"}],"y":-1041.5390624999991,"opacity":100,"height":28,"width":178,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":156088147},{"seed":2105495571,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"4EDl9H41rFwkwm0VCK9qE","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198065,"locked":false,"text":"THE OT FLOW","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3O","roundness":null,"containerId":"zZGDB1rEzfODCa0RD4O6R","originalText":"THE OT FLOW","height":16.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#fed7aa","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1603503475,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":412.43299865722656,"angle":0,"y":-1035.6640624999991,"width":95.134002685546875},{"seed":2145506739,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"OELQOFjJ7gJI_6vsuGr4b","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"1. Client applies op locally (optimistic)\n2. Sends op to Collab Node\n3. Node sequences op (assigns rev#)\n4. Transforms concurrent ops via OT\n5. Persists to op log\n6. Broadcasts transformed op to peers\n7. Peers apply op to their local doc","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3P","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Client applies op locally (optimistic)\n2. Sends op to Collab Node\n3. Node sequences op (assigns rev#)\n4. Transforms concurrent ops via OT\n5. Persists to op log\n6. Broadcasts transformed op to peers\n7. Peers apply op to their local doc","height":131.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":736187635,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":371,"angle":0,"y":-1005.5390624999991,"width":289.90481567382812},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#93c5fd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3Q","backgroundColor":"#1E3A5F","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"7mS7obBCk_F-t-yWmtlju","x":371,"seed":1260562259,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"dck1wKgRV6hj6oVy_PJQG"}],"y":-857.53906249999909,"opacity":100,"height":28,"width":178,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":2101405629},{"seed":1167607027,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"dck1wKgRV6hj6oVy_PJQG","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198065,"locked":false,"text":"WHY SHARD BY DOC","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3R","roundness":null,"conta