breaks first.\nFor Google Docs, the collab node\nis that path. It is stateful,\ncentralized per shard, and CPU-\nbound under high concurrency.\nAll four bottlenecks flow from this.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4A","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Every distributed system has a\ncritical path that breaks first.\nFor Google Docs, the collab node\nis that path. It is stateful,\ncentralized per shard, and CPU-\nbound under high concurrency.\nAll four bottlenecks flow from this.","height":131.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":105682013,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":371,"angle":0,"y":-215.53906249999909,"width":258.25482177734375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#fed7aa","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4B","backgroundColor":"#5C3D1A","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"ufFW7oFC9b-sPmlFh7dTu","x":371,"seed":1267991475,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"A_bUIwXUjYUKtFQVAY_8s"}],"y":-105.53906249999909,"opacity":100,"height":28,"width":178,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1102785523},{"seed":2086606163,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"A_bUIwXUjYUKtFQVAY_8s","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198076,"locked":false,"text":"FIX SUMMARY","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4C","roundness":null,"containerId":"ufFW7oFC9b-sPmlFh7dTu","originalText":"FIX SUMMARY","height":16.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#fed7aa","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":777894547,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":413.88899993896484,"angle":0,"y":-99.664062499999091,"width":92.222000122070312},{"seed":823587571,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"B43Nxzmt8CMawW-xwRhdB","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"B1 Hot Doc: Fan-out service\nbroadcasts to peers independently.\nCollab node only sequences + stores.\n\nB2 SPOF: Primary + standby collab\nnodes with Raft consensus. Failover\nin < 1 second, state replicated.\n\nB3 Op Log: Snapshot every 1000 ops.\nOpen doc = load snapshot + tail.\n\nB4 WS: Consistent hash gateway,\ncollab node address in Zookeeper.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4D","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"B1 Hot Doc: Fan-out service\nbroadcasts to peers independently.\nCollab node only sequences + stores.\n\nB2 SPOF: Primary + standby collab\nnodes with Raft consensus. Failover\nin < 1 second, state replicated.\n\nB3 Op Log: Snapshot every 1000 ops.\nOpen doc = load snapshot + tail.\n\nB4 WS: Consistent hash gateway,\ncollab node address in Zookeeper.","height":243.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":737621395,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":371,"angle":0,"y":-69.539062499999091,"width":276.7947998046875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#93c5fd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4E","backgroundColor":"#1E3A5F","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"WvpNho8IUTegE2KFRWaSk","x":371,"seed":1782717587,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"XCUsF3UDDGQ8jyBaBkE1v"}],"y":166.46093750000091,"opacity":100,"height":28,"width":178,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":443474205},{"seed":1402409523,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"XCUsF3UDDGQ8jyBaBkE1v","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":10