5. Cost (efficiency)\n\nWhen trade-offs conflict, higher\npriority wins. Example: Raft adds\ncost (#5) but buys availability (#3).","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAW","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Google Docs prioritises:\n1. Correctness (no silent data loss)\n2. Latency (< 100ms collab)\n3. Availability (99.99% uptime)\n4. Scale (1B users)\n5. Cost (efficiency)\n\nWhen trade-offs conflict, higher\npriority wins. Example: Raft adds\ncost (#5) but buys availability (#3).","height":187.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":165413437,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":371,"angle":0,"y":4856.4609375000009,"width":267.40484619140625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#c4b5fd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAX","backgroundColor":"#2D1B69","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"Z0hUVbyWYLZB1TkmetNhq","x":371,"seed":809762803,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"6lgpxN5AemGiCEwR5kscN"}],"y":5012.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":28,"width":148,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":327814163},{"seed":2051377555,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"6lgpxN5AemGiCEwR5kscN","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198079,"locked":false,"text":"OT VS CRDT","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAY","roundness":null,"containerId":"Z0hUVbyWYLZB1TkmetNhq","originalText":"OT VS CRDT","height":16.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#c4b5fd","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":700092275,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":401.84000015258789,"angle":0,"y":5018.3359375000009,"width":86.319999694824219},{"seed":1252319027,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"CS9nmgwEiFfoCGy7zVVW6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"This is the trade-off interviewers\nlove most. OT needs a central\nsequencer (Google has one) and\nhas lower per-char overhead.\nCRDT is decentralised but each\ncharacter carries a unique logical\nclock — expensive at document scale.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAZ","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"This is the trade-off interviewers\nlove most. OT needs a central\nsequencer (Google has one) and\nhas lower per-char overhead.\nCRDT is decentralised but each\ncharacter carries a unique logical\nclock — expensive at document scale.","height":131.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2100629939,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":371,"angle":0,"y":5048.4609375000009,"width":273.02984619140625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#93c5fd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAa","backgroundColor":"#1E3A5F","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"8kMUjk9fXzsN0hFmE-OJX","x":371,"seed":734560467,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"bd5CqrsdbwopUdELG3Il6"}],"y":5166.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":28,"width":178,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1772377853},{"seed":390524531,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"bd5CqrsdbwopUdELG3Il6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198079,"locked":false,"text":"INTERVIEW INSIGHT","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAb","roundness":null,"containerId":"8kMUjk9fXzsN0hFmE-OJX","originalTe