dated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"Everything You Need to Ace the Interview","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAh","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Everything You Need to Ace the Interview","height":37.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1027678259,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-389,"angle":0,"y":5606.4609375000009,"width":618.23980712890625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAi","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"Q-M48GaFJa9rdJM7_n7ex","x":-389,"seed":812400083,"boundElements":[],"y":5658.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":310,"width":338,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":184971389},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAj","backgroundColor":"#5C3D1A","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"2A5F-6WHqU7nSfDUMlNXx","x":-372,"seed":711658355,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"GgjBSQ7ZDjmKs1fJ93or4"}],"y":5668.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":30,"width":295,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1664393683},{"seed":1115628819,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"GgjBSQ7ZDjmKs1fJ93or4","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198079,"locked":false,"text":"OPENING STATEMENT","version":8,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAk","roundness":null,"containerId":"2A5F-6WHqU7nSfDUMlNXx","originalText":"OPENING STATEMENT","height":17.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":29311059,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-306.27399444580078,"angle":0,"y":5674.7109375000009,"width":163.54798889160156},{"seed":538905267,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"cZkMWDJEoNU2c15m72x_O","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198056,"locked":false,"text":"'Google Docs is a real-time\ncollaborative text editor. The core\nchallenge is NOT storage — it is\nconflict-free concurrent editing\nunder 100ms with zero data loss.\n\nThe system has three layers:\n- Stateful collab layer (OT engine)\n- Async fan-out (Pub\/Sub)\n- Durable storage (Bigtable + GCS)\n\nI will walk you through each.'","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAl","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"'Google Docs is a real-time\ncollaborative text editor. The core\nchallenge is NOT storage — it is\nconflict-free concurrent editing\nunder 100ms with zero data loss.\n\nThe system has three layers:\n- Stateful collab layer (OT engine)\n- Async fan-out (Pub\/Sub)\n- Durable storage (Bigtable + GCS)\n\nI will walk you through each.'","height":210,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1026715133,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-372,"angle":0,"y":5706.4609375000009,"width":240.37974548339844},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f87171","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAm","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198056,"id":"K-Zq3GmIMBhHGOtAWg9mz","x":-41,"seed":938556499,"boundElements":[],"y":5658.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":310,"width":352,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1745725021},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeC