ps\/sec\nOp log:      172 TB\/day growth\nDoc store:   ~1 Petabyte total\nCollab nodes: ~500\nGateway nodes: ~500\nSnapshot:    every 1000 ops\nFailover:    < 3 seconds (Raft)","height":210,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":356005181,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-24,"angle":0,"y":5706.4609375000009,"width":245.74168395996094},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#86efac","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAq","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"lreoUHL_e3ZaC6DUK-Sq6","x":-389,"seed":935525075,"boundElements":[],"y":5978.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":330,"width":338,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":561940755},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#86efac","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAr","backgroundColor":"#1A4D2E","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"np9z37Nq79EL7EDNxPKMm","x":-372,"seed":1910646899,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"5mfUK9grh_yBs_lfP9ppt"}],"y":5988.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":30,"width":295,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":576226717},{"seed":655008275,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"5mfUK9grh_yBs_lfP9ppt","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198079,"locked":false,"text":"OT ALGORITHM WALKTHROUGH","version":8,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAs","roundness":null,"containerId":"np9z37Nq79EL7EDNxPKMm","originalText":"OT ALGORITHM WALKTHROUGH","height":17.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#86efac","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":802391955,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-337.76701354980469,"angle":0,"y":5994.7109375000009,"width":226.53402709960938},{"seed":1077077939,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"X5KBD_owVbVl691QGGqTu","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"Doc: 'Hello World' (rev 0)\n\nUser A: Insert('X', pos=5, rev=0)\nUser B: Insert('Y', pos=5, rev=0)\n\nServer sequences A first.\nA applied -> 'HellXo World' (rev 1)\n\nOT transforms B:\npos=5 -> pos=6 (A inserted before)\nB' = Insert('Y', pos=6, rev=1)\nB' applied -> 'HellXoY World' (rev 2)\n\nBoth clients converge. Always.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAt","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Doc: 'Hello World' (rev 0)\n\nUser A: Insert('X', pos=5, rev=0)\nUser B: Insert('Y', pos=5, rev=0)\n\nServer sequences A first.\nA applied -> 'HellXo World' (rev 1)\n\nOT transforms B:\npos=5 -> pos=6 (A inserted before)\nB' = Insert('Y', pos=6, rev=1)\nB' applied -> 'HellXoY World' (rev 2)\n\nBoth clients converge. Always.","height":245,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1540344317,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-372,"angle":0,"y":6026.4609375000009,"width":242.24171447753906},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#5eead4","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAu","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"rdOdSzLV2eF2b3sj4SIBT","x":-41,"seed":1132558675,"boundElements":[],"y":5978.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":330,"width":352,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1634181203},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#5eead4","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAv","backgroundColor":"#1A4D4D","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"gQS83eOqyzxWQ410SyH_u","x":-24,"seed":776787699,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"wQ3g23oqWWQsanJlN4bLo"}],"y":5988.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":30,"width":295,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":44008029},{"seed":253460627,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"wQ3g23oqWWQsanJlN4bLo","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198079,"locked":false,"text":"WRITE PATH (say this cold)","version":8,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAw","roundness":null,"containerId":"gQS83eOqyzxWQ410SyH_u","originalText":"WRITE PATH (say this cold)","height":17.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5eead4","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1505959219,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":23.763992309570312,"angle":0,"y":5994.7109375000009,"width":199.47201538085938},{"seed":1604580915,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"axPtv4DNzPBwElFusEWSS","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"1. Client applies op locally (optimistic)\n2. Sends op via WSS to WS Gateway\n3. Gateway routes by docID hash\n4. Collab Node receives op\n5. OT transforms against concurrent ops\n6. Assigns revision number\n7. Raft quorum write (2 of 3 nodes)\n8. Publishes to Cloud Pub\/Sub\n9. Fan-out Service broadcasts\n10. Peers receive + apply op\n\nTotal: < 100ms end-to-end","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bAx","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. Client applies op locally (optimistic)\n2. Sends op via WSS to WS Gateway\n3. Gateway routes by docID hash\n4. Collab Node receives op\n5. OT transforms against concurrent ops\n6. Assigns revision number\n7. Raft quorum write (2 of 3 nodes)\n8. Publishes to Cloud Pub\/Sub\n9. Fan-out Service broadcasts\n10. Peers receive + apply op\n\nTotal: < 100ms end-to-end","height":210,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":999894717,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-24,"angle":0,"y":6026.4609375000009,"width":282.1837158203125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#a78bfa","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAy","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"PIc6hVz0Al3N5lDPw_Ii8","x":-389,"seed":516732883,"boundElements":[],"y":6318.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":290,"width":338,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1222895507},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#a78bfa","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bAz","backgroundColor":"#2D1B69","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"KMekn35HoipLbxXbBRy8S","x":-372,"seed":715933043,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"naXZ8-cd2utoq-7pzh2Rq"}],"y":6328.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":30,"width":295,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":358502173},{"seed":1518935827,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"naXZ8-cd2utoq-7pzh2Rq","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198080,"locked":false,"text":"OT VS CRDT (say this cold)","version":8,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bB0","roundness":null,"containerId":"KMekn35HoipLbxXbBRy8S","originalText":"OT VS CRDT (say this cold)","height":17.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a78bfa","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2020540115,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-323.71100616455078,"angle":0,"y":6334.7109375000009,"width":198.42201232910156},{"seed":1490666675,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"GWEocMz8GdvCOTYirhNVw","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"OT (Google Docs):\n+ Simpler data model\n+ Lower memory per char\n- Requires central sequencer\n- Cannot do P2P collab\n\nCRDT (Figma, Notion, Linear):\n+ Fully decentralised\n+ Works offline natively\n- Each char needs unique ID\n- Higher memory overhead\n- Complex merge semantics\n\nWe chose OT because Google\nhas a central server we trust.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bB1","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"OT (Google Docs):\n+ Simpler data model\n+ Lower memory per char\n- Requires central sequencer\n- Cannot do P2P collab\n\nCRDT (Figma, Notion, Linear):\n+ Fully decentralised\n+ Works offline natively\n- Each char needs unique ID\n- Higher memory overhead\n- Complex merge semantics\n\nWe chose OT because Google\nhas a central server we trust.","height":262.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1314939773,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-372,"angle":0,"y":6366.4609375000009,"width":204.87576293945312},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#c4b5fd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bB2","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"oMtf6M7KL-0aVkKqYMe-n","x":-41,"seed":1027913299,"boundElements":[],"y":6318.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":290,"width":352,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":283598547},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#c4b5fd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bB3","backgroundColor":"#2D1B69","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"BlQxmbw5SE_VSlzt62eob","x":-24,"seed":1721791475,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"YTdyspgThW7G6cxrYJvCu"}],"y":6328.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":30,"width":295,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1524689885},{"seed":351501715,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"YTdyspgThW7G6cxrYJvCu","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198080,"locked":false,"text":"BOTTLENECK ANSWERS","version":8,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bB4","roundness":null,"containerId":"BlQxmbw5SE_VSlzt62eob","originalText":"BOTTLENECK ANSWERS","height":17.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#c4b5fd","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1181592691,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":37.722000122070312,"angle":0,"y":6334.7109375000009,"width":171.55599975585938},{"seed":1131696947,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"Kg8kbI7-OCwMMh-Ng_b7c","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1773086198057,"locked":false,"text":"Q: What if collab node crashes?\nA: Raft promotes standby in < 3s.\n   Clients buffer + OT-rebase.\n\nQ: What if a doc has 1000 editors?\nA: Rate limit ops. Drop cursor\n   storms. Coalesce edits.\n   Optimistic apply hides latency.\n\nQ: How does offline editing work?\nA: Buffer ops locally. On reconnect\n   send last rev#. Server replies\n   with missed ops. Client rebases\n   local buffer (like git rebase).\n\nQ: How do you open a large doc fast?\nA: Snapshot + tail. < 200ms.","version":6,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bB5","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Q: What if collab node crashes?\nA: Raft promotes standby in < 3s.\n   Clients buffer + OT-rebase.\n\nQ: What if a doc has 1000 editors?\nA: Rate limit ops. Drop cursor\n   storms. Coalesce edits.\n   Optimistic apply hides latency.\n\nQ: How does offline editing work?\nA: Buffer ops locally. On reconnect\n   send last rev#. Server replies\n   with missed ops. Client rebases\n   local buffer (like git rebase).\n\nQ: How do you open a large doc fast?\nA: Snapshot + tail. < 200ms.","height":297.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a0a0a0","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":720463933,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-24,"angle":0,"y":6366.4609375000009,"width":257.12371826171875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bB6","backgroundColor":"#0d1117","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"yES0Y2qYTsxokIqPDEE8u","x":-389,"seed":1116304595,"boundElements":[],"y":6618.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":120,"width":700,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1164314131},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"bB7","backgroundColor":"#5C3D1A","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":6,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1773086198057,"id":"Y2D63XhF_ekUaCQ5AC8rz","x":-372,"seed":298410611,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"xZLFH93q9N3V2uiMqiMPK"}],"y":6628.4609375000009,"opacity":100,"height":30,"width":295,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":812865693},{"seed":2046467091,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"xZLFH93q9N3V2uiMqiMPK","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1773086198080,"locked":false,"text":"MENTAL MODELS TO MEMORISE","version":8,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index"